{"type": "email", "id": "email_001", "subject": "Weekly Sales Team Meeting", "from": "amanda.lee@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "Amanda Lee", "to": ["james.clark@elexionauto.com", "sarah.johnson@elexionauto.com", "michael.roberts@elexionauto.com", "jessica.martin@elexionauto.com", "david.williams@elexionauto.com", "maria.garcia@elexionauto.com", "john.miller@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2023-04-01 08:30:00", "body": "Team, our weekly sales meeting is scheduled for this Friday at 10 a.m. Please prepare your reports on current sales activities and any issues you may have encountered. Looking forward to seeing you all.", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "Q2 Budget Planning", "from": "amanda.lee@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "Amanda Lee", "to": ["john.miller@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2023-04-02 10:15:00", "body": "John, I need your input on the Q2 budget allocation for our department. Can we arrange a meeting to discuss this? Let me know your availability.", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "New CRM Training Session", "from": "amanda.lee@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "Amanda Lee", "to": ["james.clark@elexionauto.com", "sarah.johnson@elexionauto.com", "michael.roberts@elexionauto.com", "jessica.martin@elexionauto.com", "david.williams@elexionauto.com", "maria.garcia@elexionauto.com", "john.miller@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2023-04-03 13:00:00", "body": "All, there will be a training session next week on how to use our new CRM system. The session is mandatory. More details will follow soon.", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_004", "subject": "Performance Review Schedule", "from": "amanda.lee@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "Amanda Lee", "to": ["john.miller@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2023-04-04 15:30:00", "body": "John, I am planning the schedule for the upcoming performance reviews. Can we meet to discuss the timelines and key performance indicators? Thanks.", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_005", "subject": "Update on the Annual Automotive Trade Show", "from": "amanda.lee@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "Amanda Lee", "to": ["sarah.johnson@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2023-04-05 09:00:00", "body": "Sarah, could you please update me on our preparations for the annual automotive trade show? I want to ensure our participation is as effective as possible.", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_001", "subject": "Quarterly CRM Activity Summary", "from": "amanda.lee@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "Amanda Lee", "to": ["james.clark@elexionauto.com", "sarah.johnson@elexionauto.com", "michael.roberts@elexionauto.com", "jessica.martin@elexionauto.com", "david.williams@elexionauto.com", "maria.garcia@elexionauto.com", "john.miller@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2024-11-30 16:00:00", "body": "Dear Team,

I hope this email finds you well. As we are approaching the end of the year, I would like to share with you some important data related to our CRM activities.

Our CRM system has been working quite effectively. Between February and November 2024, it sent 19,255 automated email notifications to you about lead activities. This high degree of automation has allowed us to focus more on closing deals rather than managing leads manually.

It is crucial that we continue leveraging our CRM capabilities to better understand our customers' behavior. I strongly encourage you to keep tracking such notifications and ensure every lead is followed up.

Best,
Amanda Lee", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "Re: Quarterly CRM Activity Summary", "from": "james.clark@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "James Clark", "to": ["amanda.lee@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2024-12-01 08:10:00", "body": "Hi Amanda,

Thanks for the summary. The automated notifications have indeed been very helpful in keeping up with the leads. It's great to see the CRM system working so efficiently.

Regards,
James Clark", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "Re: Quarterly CRM Activity Summary", "from": "sarah.johnson@elexionauto.com", "from_name": "Sarah Johnson", "to": ["amanda.lee@elexionauto.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2024-12-01 09:25:00", "body": "Hi Amanda,

I agree with James. The CRM system has been instrumental in helping us track and manage leads. The data-driven insights have significantly improved our sales process. Looking forward to more such insights in the future.

Best,
Sarah Johnson", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
